Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 1st, 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As usual, Hinazuki was standing\Nalone in this park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it was a little before six.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the time,\NI was on my way to the hideout.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went looking for my missing gloves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't remember\Nif the gloves were actually there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After leaving the hideout,\NI looked towards the bank{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and saw Yuuki sitting there,\Nfacing the river.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, when I cut back\Nthrough the park,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki was gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.57,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}February 24th{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all eyes on the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kayo Hinazuki is going to be the first victim\Nin a series of kidnappings and murders,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a week from now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:01:00.01,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MARCH
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Safely getting through March 1st{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and spending the next day\Nwith Hinazuki at my birthday party...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would definitely change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make sure\Nthose crimes never happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:30.22,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}February 25th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast will be ready in a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd all go\Nto the Science Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a date,\NI'd give you money for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a date, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have hot pot or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki will be here\Nfor the birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Hinazuki, from the fifth block.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's already asking me\Nleading questions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful when you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry up and eat your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.53,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Liveman" is starting soon! Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "falcon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hunting bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saturday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to take Hinazuki away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from her house or,\Nmore precisely, her mother's abuse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Sensei!\N- Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this, so explain it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It ticks me off\Nhow they're all so flirty with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You know everything, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you were the same way, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can go up there, too, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, "y'know"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to sound cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei thinks I'm a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go\Nto the Science Center on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ask Hinazuki, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do that day\Nand I can't get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got somethin' important\Nto do, so I can't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go, but I've got\Nsomething to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for just you and Hinazuki to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told them I couldn't play on Saturday\Nbecause I have a date with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I say that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did say that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my mother told me to get home\Nearly on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I wanna take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop by the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in two children\Ngoing out somewhere together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't just be to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a learning experience, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can learn at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo helps me at home on Saturdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Helps? With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Helps you blow off steam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not obliged to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want Hinazuki\Nto stay home so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of several reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For one, you're both children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen,\Nwho would take responsibility?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's turning it against me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taking my surly daughter somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you stand to gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to saving a friend,\Nthere are no gains or losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saving Kayo from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're a prince\Non a white horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have hinted at her abuse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get your minds out of the gutter,\Nyou perverted brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ms. Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't call children "perverted brats."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms... Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say half of it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see, my son shows motivation\Nin everything he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm his parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think your household\Nand mine are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you visit for a chat next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saturday... I'll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I butt in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got off work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's lucky that I happened to see you two\Nand followed you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You followed us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm kidding, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... well, everything\Nshould be okay for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was actually\Nwearing nice clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the mother\Ncares about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}HINAZUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But between our conversation\Nand seeing the mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She didn't work for a TV news\Ndepartment for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo is a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I embarrassed for?\NI'm 29 years old!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abandon her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:07.14,LowSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,February 27th - Saturday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}February 27th, Saturday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It's a clear day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems Hinazuki's mother has refrained\Nfrom physical abuse for the past several days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's hardly anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it exciting, like we just snuck in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I see somebody else, I hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She didn't say, "Are you stupid?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}PLANETARIUM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see the planetarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We saw plenty of stars last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it déjà vu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I often came here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it's my first time with Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for inviting me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know I liked this place, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that why I chose this place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do people who want to make manga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do people who want to make manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tend to come to places like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tend to come to places like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember this same\Nconversation from 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came here alone then\Nand ran into Hinazuki by chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe there is a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I repeating the same time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I intend to change the future,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I've unwittingly been riding\Nthe same rail of time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki, I'll carry your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can change a lot\Nthrough my own behavior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I mustered\Nthe courage and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finished what I had to do early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There. It's changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru is a gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.99,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4\NAccomplishment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.00,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5th Grade, Class 4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning, Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Monday, but she's not late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I actually said that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you just hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:43.23,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,February 29th
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh my God!\N- Satoru's got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gonna get married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! First they gotta get engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?\N- Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}HOPE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki is due to be murdered tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 1st.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the real showdown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hinazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up at your house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll stop by tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left the house a little early.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}March 1st, 1988.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day Hinazuki\Ndisappeared 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But today is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki isn't going anywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- Morning!\N- Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Circumstances have changed a lot\Nbetween 18 years ago and now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru's got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki was targeted{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because she was\Nalways alone in the park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys all\Nbetter be there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure!\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those circumstances\Ndisappeared days ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's stop at the children's center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm with her today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that. Hang out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I win again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's still fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.45,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RESTAURANT ROW
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Answer the questions below:\NQuestion 1: Make a sentence using the word "pole" in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The polar bear from the North Pole ate the teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The polar bear from the North Pole ate the teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Answer the questions below:\NQuestion 1: Make a sentence using the word "pole" in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up tomorrow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said it as loud as I could.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was for Hinazuki,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her mother inside,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and anyone else who may\Nhave been listening nearby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was saying that I'm here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-day is almost over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got through it this easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coming here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this one day,\NI definitely changed history.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even six yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I couldn't sleep a wink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And at that moment, I wanted to see\NHinazuki's face as soon as possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone still okay for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go to your\Nhouse and par-tay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all go shopping first—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satoru! Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come here. I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why today of all days?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because we blew off\Nthe last cleaning duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of cold-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.69,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAKAI SUPERMARKET
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.69,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BARGAIN SALE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly 5,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, it was 5,000 yen\Non the nose 18 years ago, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in such high spirits\Nbecause of my birthday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I spent all the money I had.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Mom and I make tons of sandwiches,\Nbut just the two of us ate them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SATORU & HINAZUKI\NHAPPY BIRTHDAY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru! Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You secretly made all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They said they wanted to do it\Nthemselves, so I gave them a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the after school duty, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. We asked Mr. Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He told us it was Hinazuki's birthday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.78,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy Birthday\NSatoru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:12.08,LowSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy Birthday\NKayo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did want to surprise you a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Satoru insisted on getting two cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have time to finish your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you working on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wanted to go home early for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I almost had it done last night,\Nbut I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make sandwiches\Nwith 5,000 yen worth of ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You used all the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a lot of fun\Nmaking sandwiches together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unlike 18 years ago,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we finished them all off in one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fun having friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki and I got\Nseveral presents from everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Walk Hinazuki home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the others, too...\NI'm glad we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you your present tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I changed history!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I got home,\Neveryone had already gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My exhaustion from the day before\Nhad reached its peak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my tense feelings\Nrelaxed all at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I collapsed then and there\Nand slept like a log.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIKOTO ELEMENTARY SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap! I'm late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to mark you as tardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Safe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kayo the only one who's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki didn't come\Nto school the next day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last promise made between me\Nand Hinazuki was never fulfilled.{\i0}
